_:Nd316f574fae74cca9a9044a63c8d4521 <http://schema.org/description> "The Women and Equalities Unit is part of the Office for Equality and Opportunity. We lead work on policy relating to gender equality, LGBT+ people and the overall framework of equality legislation in the UK." .
